			Child Sponsorship</h1>

			<h4>School of Hope Student Sponsorship</h4>
			<p>
				Students in this program come to school each day and then return home to live in the village with their families. Student sponsorship is $35 per month or $420 annually. Your sponsorship funds provide your Haitian student with a quality Christ-centered education. Sponsorship funds go toward:
			</p>
			<ul class="learnSponsor">
				<li>
					Daily nutritious meal
				</li>
				<li>
					Christ-centered curriculum and teacher training
				</li>
				<li>
					School-specific improvement initiatives
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				Sponsors can choose a boy or girl student at the Kindergarten, Primary (Elementary) or Secondary (Jr. and Sr. High) grade levels. Once a sponsor is connected with their student, they will receive a profile card with a photo and personal information about their sponsored child. 
			</p>
			<p>
				<strong>What You’ll Receive From Your Child:</strong>
			</p>
			<ul class="learnSponsor">
				<li>Annual photo</li>
				<li>School updates throughout the year</li>
				<li>Reply letters to any correspondence you send to your student </li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				<strong>Ways to Connect With Your Child:</strong>
			</p>
			<ul class="learnSponsor">
				<li>
					Send letters and photographs online
				</li>
				<li>
					Give them a gift through our online store
				</li>
				<li>
					Visit your child in Haiti on a Mission Trip!
				</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="buttonSquareOrange" style="width: 200px; margin:10px 0 40px 0;">
				<a href="http://mohhaiti.force.com/sponsorship">Sponsor a student &raquo;</a>
			</div>
			<h4>Village of Hope Orphan Sponsorship</h4>
			<p>
				Village of Hope children are in the loving care of Mission of Hope full time. The children are raised in a Godly, loving home environment. Sponsorship cost is $150 per month and your Village of Hope sponsorship funds help cover day-to-day living expenses such as:
			</p>
			<ul class="learnSponsor" style="margin-top: -15px;">
				<li>
					Lodging
				</li>
				<li>
					Food
				</li>
				<li>
					Routine medical care
				</li>
				<li>
					Staff salaries (caregivers/mommies, cooks, etc…)
				</li>
				<li>
					Clothing/shoes
				</li>
				<li>
					Fuel to generate electrical power and more!
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				Once a sponsor is connected with their child they will receive a photo of and information about their sponsored child, as well as Village of Hope updates and crafts from their child throughout the year. If you are interested in sponsoring an orphan at our Village of Hope, please contact us at 512-256-0835 or email sponsorship@mohhaiti.org.
			</p>
			<p>
				<strong>What You’ll Receive From Your Child:</strong>
			</p>
			<ul class="learnSponsor">
				<li>Introductory photo and biography</li>
				<li>Annually updated photo</li>
				<li>Christmas card and photo</li>
				<li>Seasonal crafts and notes</li>
			<!--<li>Thank You Cards and Photos in Response</li> -->
			</ul>
			<p>
				<strong>Ways to Connect With Your Child:</strong>
			</p>
			<ul class="learnSponsor">
				<li>
					Send letters, cards, and photographs
				</li>
				<li>
					Give them a gift through our online store
				</li>
				<li>
					Visit your child in Haiti on a Mission Trip!
				</li>
			</ul>
		
